<p class="ayah 52-43" id="43" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَيْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">other than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُبْحَـٰنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Glory be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُشْرِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they associate (with Him).</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>43<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
